{"tid":1185790,"cid":36,"subCid":0,"title":"乙型肝炎帶菌者請進","createTime":"2019-06-04T13:06:46.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-03T15:14:57.000Z","uid":88147,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":24,"replies":[{"pid":"510391356cd5e5cadb4958b40c6d9a56b9313315","tid":1185790,"uid":88147,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-04T13:06:46.000Z","msg":"最近去私家醫院做第一次bodycheck<br />\n點知咁唔好彩發現我自己係乙型肝炎帶菌者<br />\n而且入面嘅細胞超過左一定嘅數量<br />\n個醫生同我講需要食藥治療控制<br />\n因為佢呢間醫院提供唔到食藥嘅服務<br />\n所以我自己上網睇但係發覺搵唔到 <br />\n唯一都係灣仔家計會 睇完醫生check多次可以食藥<br />\n我想問吓咁多位有呢個病嘅巴絲 <br />\n你哋係點樣食藥？<br />\n 家計會或拎醫生紙係街度買？"},{"pid":"fbe17c154812afb061513e535d8b37b129c167b7","tid":1185790,"uid":74334,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-06-04T13:15:06.000Z","msg":"咁多年黎有乙肝但唔駛食藥但keep住半年/一年覆診<br />\n早幾個月驗血驗到有少少乙肝抗體，話我已經冇左乙肝"},{"pid":"bc20ae7a998eff65e353ab15e4b79976fad16cdb","tid":1185790,"uid":252917,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-04T13:16:12.000Z","msg":"有藥食架咩<br />\n我都無理佢好耐"},{"pid":"68eec62c4e2a4490fb73ce9f5d608897e43101b5","tid":1185790,"uid":144883,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-04T13:27:51.000Z","msg":"要食藥㗎咩，乙肝帶菌其實喺香港好普遍<br />\n尤其50-60年代出生果批"},{"pid":"77dfb6fe93148ac421a88d94b391e4be38ec59ae","tid":1185790,"uid":224066,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-04T13:34:18.000Z","msg":"香港有60萬人帶乙肝病毒<br />\n[url]<a href=\"https://orientaldaily.on.cc/cnt/news/20170122/mobile/odn-20170122-0122_00176_002.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Forientaldaily.on.cc%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20170122%2Fmobile%2Fodn-20170122-0122_00176_002.html&d=nhC78NoCA6QB0w8lKR9CgiEyVFbloTKGHdwbQdNTMZo%3D&h=82d8e68b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://orientaldaily.on.cc/cnt/news/20170122/mobile/odn-20170122-0122_00176_002.html</a><br />\n[/url]<br />\n<br />\n港人成全球最長壽 力壓日本再奪冠<br />\n<a href=\"https://topick.hket.com/article/2120449/%E6%B8%AF%E4%BA%BA%E6%88%90%E5%85%A8%E7%90%83%E6%9C%80%E9